<h2 id="instances">1. Instances</h2>
<p>
    All entities are data records that can be displayed on their own page
    (for <a href="Instanzen.aspx">examples</a> there is a page with random links).
</p>
<p>
    In the database tables, the key fields are GUIDs. These are used in URIrefs
    and URLs. A URIref in an RDF statement consists of the base namespace
    (<a href="https://nulllogicone.net/">https://nulllogicone.net/</a>) followed by the
    full class name from [SAPCT][NKBZ] with appended GUID. These can display further information
    on a webpage as URLs.
</p>
