<h2 id="importexport">4. Input / Output</h2>
<p>
    Data can be exchanged and distributed in RDF format. For this purpose, functions are
    summarized on the <a href="RDF/default.aspx"><strong>Input / Output</strong></a> page
    that output instances from [SAPCT] as RDF documents,
    validate these documents, and parse them back into objects. The data objects
    can then be easily stored in a DBMS or serialized as XML.
</p>
<p>
    In addition, the entire Word Space can be output as an RDF file.
</p>

